WEBVTT

00:00:04.380 --> 00:00:09.677
Is the destiny of mankind controlled
by some transcendental entity or Law?

00:00:10.511 --> 00:00:13.556
Is it like the hand of
God hovering above?

00:00:14.557 --> 00:00:16.475
At least, it is true...

00:00:16.892 --> 00:00:20.479
...that man has no
control, even over his own will.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:00:42.918 --> 00:00:44.920
<i>Feel no shame about shape.</i>

00:00:45.087 --> 00:00:46.839
<i>Weather changes the phrase.</i>

00:00:47.048 --> 00:00:50.593
<i>Even mother will
show you another way.</i>

00:00:50.801 --> 00:00:52.970
<i>So, put your glasses on.</i>

00:00:53.095 --> 00:00:55.097
<i>Nothing will be wrong.</i>

00:00:55.222 --> 00:00:57.224
<i>There's no blame, there's no fame.</i>

00:00:57.433 --> 00:00:59.101
<i>It's up to you.</i>

00:00:59.351 --> 00:01:02.730
<i>The first words should be found.</i>

00:01:03.439 --> 00:01:06.317
<i>Whatever holds you back.</i>

00:01:07.151 --> 00:01:07.818
<i>I...</i>

00:01:08.152 --> 00:01:08.903
<i>... can...</i>

00:01:09.028 --> 00:01:11.072
<i>I can get it off.</i>

00:01:11.197 --> 00:01:12.073
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:12.281 --> 00:01:13.032
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:13.199 --> 00:01:14.909
<i>Tell me what you want.</i>

00:01:15.076 --> 00:01:16.035
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:16.202 --> 00:01:16.952
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:17.078 --> 00:01:18.954
<i>I don't know why you are afraid.</i>

00:01:19.205 --> 00:01:20.081
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:20.289 --> 00:01:21.082
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:21.332 --> 00:01:22.792
<i>Tell me what you'd say.</i>

00:01:23.042 --> 00:01:24.085
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:24.293 --> 00:01:25.211
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:25.336 --> 00:01:25.961
<i>Too late...</i>

00:01:26.087 --> 00:01:27.671
<i>It's too late.</i>

00:01:32.593 --> 00:01:36.597
The Band of the Hawk

00:01:41.977 --> 00:01:43.312
Charge!

00:01:43.437 --> 00:01:45.231
Off with the general's head!

00:01:45.356 --> 00:01:47.233
Win as much reward as you could want!

00:02:06.127 --> 00:02:07.628
B-Bazuso!

00:02:07.878 --> 00:02:09.880
The Gray Knight, Bazuso!

00:02:10.172 --> 00:02:13.175
As long as I stand here,
no one will be able to pass!

00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:16.053
Who else wants to feel the
blade of my axe against their neck?

00:02:16.512 --> 00:02:19.682
Is he the Bazuso who is
known for slaying thirty men at once?

00:02:19.890 --> 00:02:21.308
And for killing bears?

00:02:21.433 --> 00:02:23.769
Quit your dawdling!

00:02:23.894 --> 00:02:26.021
Defeat him and earn the bounty!

00:02:26.647 --> 00:02:28.190
He's talking nonsense.

00:02:28.315 --> 00:02:30.067
We're just mercenaries.

00:02:30.192 --> 00:02:31.777
Try doing it yourself!

00:02:41.453 --> 00:02:42.163
Who's that?

00:02:42.204 --> 00:02:43.956
Hey, he's still a kid.

00:02:44.081 --> 00:02:45.583
And look at that sword...

00:02:45.958 --> 00:02:49.086
Is the brat really going
to swing such a big blade?

00:02:49.295 --> 00:02:50.296
He's inexperienced...

00:02:50.421 --> 00:02:52.214
The sword's just for looks!

00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:53.674
He'll be killed off!

00:02:55.467 --> 00:02:57.845
Do you really want to fight with me?

00:02:58.220 --> 00:03:00.598
You've got some balls, kid.

00:03:01.182 --> 00:03:03.601
But, you're going to regret it...

00:03:03.976 --> 00:03:08.814
...when I chop your
head off with my axe!

00:03:08.981 --> 00:03:10.107
Either way...

00:03:10.191 --> 00:03:13.611
...it's pathetic that a rookie like you
is allowed to fight on the battlefield...

00:03:13.736 --> 00:03:16.822
There seems to be a serious
shortage of soldiers in your army.

00:03:17.114 --> 00:03:20.242
Or are all the men
cowards, hiding behind a kid?

00:03:26.248 --> 00:03:26.999
W-What speed!

00:03:27.124 --> 00:03:28.250
And his strength!

00:03:28.375 --> 00:03:30.336
Look, Bazuso is being forced back!

00:03:58.739 --> 00:03:59.782
W-Wait...

00:04:16.632 --> 00:04:17.758
N-Now!

00:04:17.883 --> 00:04:19.260
Everyone charge at once!

00:04:22.263 --> 00:04:24.848
I didn't know our opponents had
a warrior with such amazing skills.

00:04:25.266 --> 00:04:26.892
Is he a mercenary or something?

00:04:27.226 --> 00:04:29.353
Wondering if he's stronger than you?

00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:31.772
Fool, our leader is on a different level.

00:04:31.981 --> 00:04:33.148
Right, Griffith?

00:04:33.899 --> 00:04:34.900
Evacuate this fort.

00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:36.110
All right.

00:04:36.151 --> 00:04:39.655
We held this castle for three
months, not the three days they expected.

00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:41.907
And we helped the fief lord escape...

00:04:42.116 --> 00:04:44.618
We did the amount of
work we were paid for.

00:04:56.630 --> 00:04:58.424
Here's your reward for the battle.

00:04:58.549 --> 00:04:59.675
Check the amount.

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:01.885
I must say, I was very impressed.

00:05:02.303 --> 00:05:06.140
Even if it was just a fluke,
a rookie like you defeated Bazuso...

00:05:06.307 --> 00:05:08.309
Well, it's truly unbelievable.

00:05:08.892 --> 00:05:12.688
Would you consider
serving me regularly?

00:05:12.938 --> 00:05:15.316
Your salary could be tripled.

00:05:15.441 --> 00:05:18.152
I would even promote you
to ranked warrior if you want.

00:05:18.777 --> 00:05:21.822
Don't you think that's a deal a
mere mercenary could never resist?

00:05:22.197 --> 00:05:22.948
Don't you?

00:05:25.701 --> 00:05:27.453
Our contract expired today.

00:05:28.078 --> 00:05:31.081
It looks like the
fighting is over around here.

00:05:31.582 --> 00:05:33.042
Wait a minute...

00:05:33.167 --> 00:05:35.336
I will secure your
position and income as well.

00:05:35.461 --> 00:05:38.464
You won't need to put yourself
in danger as a grunt during the war...

00:05:39.548 --> 00:05:40.424
Hands off!

00:05:40.591 --> 00:05:41.300
But...

00:05:42.801 --> 00:05:44.595
Don't ever touch me!

00:06:11.455 --> 00:06:12.081
Hey...

00:06:12.498 --> 00:06:13.374
Someone's coming!

00:06:13.499 --> 00:06:14.124
What?

00:06:17.127 --> 00:06:17.836
Hey!

00:06:18.253 --> 00:06:21.382
Hey, isn't he the guy who beat Bazuso?

00:06:21.507 --> 00:06:22.758
What's he doing around here?

00:06:23.384 --> 00:06:24.843
He's the enemy, should we get him?

00:06:24.968 --> 00:06:27.346
It doesn't matter,
we're finished fighting, right?

00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:32.768
But, I'm sure his coin-purse is bulging.

00:06:33.602 --> 00:06:36.397
He got plenty of reward
money for defeating Bazuso.

00:06:38.524 --> 00:06:39.900
Griffith, can we get him?

00:06:44.363 --> 00:06:45.656
Do what you like.

00:06:47.366 --> 00:06:49.034
Okay guys, come with me!

00:06:50.411 --> 00:06:51.495
What?

00:06:51.870 --> 00:06:53.622
What's so funny, Caska?

00:06:54.289 --> 00:06:56.291
You can't possibly beat him.

00:06:57.042 --> 00:06:58.919
That's what you say, but...

00:06:59.128 --> 00:07:01.922
I was planning to beat
Bazuso and become famous.

00:07:02.548 --> 00:07:05.551
I won't be satisfied
unless I beat that wanderer...

00:07:05.634 --> 00:07:07.761
...who dared to spoil my reputation.

00:07:08.262 --> 00:07:08.929
You'll die...

00:07:11.890 --> 00:07:13.684
You'll see what happens.

00:07:18.147 --> 00:07:19.690
Oh boy, Corkus...

00:07:19.815 --> 00:07:22.151
Griffith, is it all right
to leave this up to him?

00:07:36.081 --> 00:07:37.332
Just my imagination?

00:07:42.713 --> 00:07:43.464
Thieves?

00:07:43.797 --> 00:07:45.090
Dan, get him!

00:07:45.215 --> 00:07:45.924
Got it!

00:08:08.614 --> 00:08:11.575
T-This guy's too strong...

00:08:11.867 --> 00:08:15.204
Look, that guy beat Dan and Earl!

00:08:15.370 --> 00:08:16.622
Dammit!

00:08:16.747 --> 00:08:18.248
What are they doing?

00:08:18.499 --> 00:08:21.585
Corkus lost his nerve, even
though he brought all this on!

00:08:21.835 --> 00:08:23.253
See, I told you so.

00:08:23.754 --> 00:08:24.630
Caska...

00:08:25.881 --> 00:08:27.633
You better help him.

00:08:27.883 --> 00:08:29.259
W-Wait a minute!

00:08:29.343 --> 00:08:30.385
Are you kidding?

00:08:30.511 --> 00:08:31.512
It's Corkus' fault!

00:08:33.805 --> 00:08:35.057
Okay, I'll do it...

00:08:39.186 --> 00:08:41.188
Hey, Riguel, you go next!

00:08:41.313 --> 00:08:42.773
W-Why should I?

00:08:55.285 --> 00:08:56.078
Caska...

00:08:56.203 --> 00:08:57.829
Y-You're backing me up?

00:08:59.331 --> 00:09:00.791
It's not for you.

00:09:00.958 --> 00:09:02.584
It was Griffith's order.

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.211
Get back...

00:09:27.109 --> 00:09:28.235
It's a girl!

00:09:30.487 --> 00:09:32.114
You bastard!

00:09:40.747 --> 00:09:41.748
Hey, look.

00:09:41.873 --> 00:09:43.750
Caska's being driven into a corner.

00:09:43.959 --> 00:09:46.503
No one except Griffith
has ever beaten Caska!

00:09:47.504 --> 00:09:48.255
His skill...

00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:49.840
And his strength...

00:09:55.137 --> 00:09:56.013
I'm going to die!

00:10:04.855 --> 00:10:05.897
Griffith!

00:10:06.148 --> 00:10:07.232
Griffith?

00:10:08.775 --> 00:10:11.028
Be careful, he's tough!

00:10:12.738 --> 00:10:14.406
Will you put up your sword?

00:10:18.994 --> 00:10:20.120
I see...

00:10:32.299 --> 00:10:32.924
What?

00:10:45.812 --> 00:10:46.772
Too quick!

00:10:55.822 --> 00:10:56.823
Amazing!

00:10:56.948 --> 00:10:57.949
In one strike...

00:10:58.075 --> 00:11:00.077
Oh, what an idiot!

00:11:00.452 --> 00:11:02.913
He's no match for
Griffith in single combat!

00:11:03.413 --> 00:11:04.414
Corkus!

00:11:04.539 --> 00:11:07.167
You are the one at fault
because you brought this on!

00:11:07.584 --> 00:11:08.960
S-Sorry.

00:11:14.716 --> 00:11:16.051
Y-You...

00:11:16.176 --> 00:11:18.053
Stand back, Caska.

00:11:36.071 --> 00:11:36.863
Griffith!

00:12:55.150 --> 00:12:56.067
Gambino!

00:12:57.944 --> 00:12:59.529
Gambino, help me!

00:12:59.654 --> 00:13:01.281
My sword is no use against this thing!

00:13:04.910 --> 00:13:05.952
Gambino?

00:13:06.328 --> 00:13:07.954
Don't talk nonsense.

00:13:09.039 --> 00:13:10.540
Don't you remember?

00:13:11.166 --> 00:13:13.335
I am no longer living in your world.

00:13:16.463 --> 00:13:19.591
You ran a sword through my body...

00:13:20.175 --> 00:13:21.301
...I was in agony...

00:13:21.718 --> 00:13:23.678
...and then I died...

00:13:26.348 --> 00:13:27.057
Gambino!

00:13:27.182 --> 00:13:28.350
Please listen, I was...

00:13:32.479 --> 00:13:34.105
Help me, Gambino!

00:13:34.731 --> 00:13:37.359
You were the one who deserved to die.

00:13:37.567 --> 00:13:38.693
You should have died.

00:13:39.736 --> 00:13:41.863
You should have died.

00:13:42.239 --> 00:13:44.324
You should have died.

00:13:44.616 --> 00:13:46.576
You should have died.

00:13:46.743 --> 00:13:48.495
You should have died.

00:13:48.620 --> 00:13:50.497
You should have died.

00:13:50.705 --> 00:13:51.748
You should have died.

00:13:52.207 --> 00:13:53.124
Forgive me!

00:13:53.333 --> 00:13:54.501
Gambino!

00:13:54.626 --> 00:13:56.253
Please!

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:04.886
Don't touch me...

00:14:05.887 --> 00:14:07.264
Don't touch me...

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.641
Don't touch me...

00:14:10.517 --> 00:14:12.727
Please don't touch me...

00:14:14.729 --> 00:14:16.273
Don't touch me...

00:14:21.653 --> 00:14:22.904
Who is this?

00:14:24.406 --> 00:14:25.657
A woman?

00:14:28.118 --> 00:14:29.619
Black eyes...

00:14:43.049 --> 00:14:44.134
Where am I?

00:15:09.075 --> 00:15:10.452
A mercenary band?

00:15:10.827 --> 00:15:12.579
They look kind of young...

00:15:19.085 --> 00:15:20.170
That guy...

00:15:27.677 --> 00:15:28.720
Black eyes...

00:15:36.603 --> 00:15:37.979
You...

00:15:38.104 --> 00:15:40.732
...should have been
killed by Griffith back there!

00:15:45.862 --> 00:15:47.364
That was no surprise...

00:15:47.614 --> 00:15:51.618
Caska is always rebelling against
her station, and her life as a mercenary.

00:15:52.369 --> 00:15:55.455
She's far more skilled
than the rest of us are...

00:15:56.957 --> 00:15:58.833
It's particularly shocking to her...

00:15:58.959 --> 00:16:01.878
...that Griffith gave her the order
to lie down by you for two days...

00:16:02.253 --> 00:16:03.755
...and warm your icy body...

00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:06.508
...since you were
shivering from the heavy bleeding.

00:16:07.133 --> 00:16:10.220
"It's a woman's duty
to warm a man," he said.

00:16:11.638 --> 00:16:13.264
Did she punch you out of bed?

00:16:16.601 --> 00:16:17.894
I am Griffith.

00:16:18.228 --> 00:16:19.145
Your name?

00:16:20.647 --> 00:16:21.398
Guts...

00:16:24.275 --> 00:16:25.986
Such a great sword...

00:16:26.111 --> 00:16:27.654
I couldn't use it.

00:16:31.157 --> 00:16:32.617
Will you follow me?

00:16:44.170 --> 00:16:45.171
Who are they...

00:16:45.296 --> 00:16:47.298
...these guys with an
unpleasant look in their eyes?

00:16:49.009 --> 00:16:50.135
The Band of the Hawk.

00:16:50.885 --> 00:16:51.928
The Band of the Hawk?

00:16:52.053 --> 00:16:53.263
Ever hear of us?

00:16:54.305 --> 00:16:55.640
I've heard only rumors...

00:16:56.307 --> 00:16:57.183
The Band of the Hawk...

00:16:57.684 --> 00:17:01.021
A mercenary company known as
the Grim Reaper on the Battlefield...

00:17:01.062 --> 00:17:04.274
Because of the Hawks, that
castle siege lasted for three months...

00:17:04.399 --> 00:17:07.027
...even though everyone
predicted that it would end in three days...

00:17:07.736 --> 00:17:11.656
After all that, I never figured
that the Hawks were just these kids.

00:17:13.533 --> 00:17:18.496
What on earth is Griffith
up to, sparing that punk's life?

00:17:18.747 --> 00:17:21.124
I assume he wants that man to join us.

00:17:22.417 --> 00:17:24.919
We saw with our own
eyes how powerful he is.

00:17:25.253 --> 00:17:27.756
I'm sure he is going to
be a fine addition to our army.

00:17:29.799 --> 00:17:32.052
Don't be ridiculous, Ricket!

00:17:32.802 --> 00:17:36.264
He cut off Earl's arm
and sent Dan to his death!

00:17:36.681 --> 00:17:39.934
The bastard killed our comrades,
I can't pretend that didn't happen!

00:17:40.685 --> 00:17:41.811
Right, Pippin?

00:17:57.577 --> 00:17:59.079
Isn't this a nice view?

00:18:01.706 --> 00:18:02.707
Why?

00:18:03.458 --> 00:18:05.960
You could have stabbed me
through the heart back there.

00:18:06.294 --> 00:18:08.171
It would have been simple for you.

00:18:08.588 --> 00:18:10.048
Why didn't you kill me?

00:18:14.719 --> 00:18:17.055
I desire to have you as my soldier.

00:18:17.222 --> 00:18:18.223
Guts...

00:18:21.184 --> 00:18:24.229
I observed the duel between
you and Bazuso at the castle.

00:18:24.354 --> 00:18:25.730
That was a superb fight...

00:18:26.731 --> 00:18:27.732
However...

00:18:37.242 --> 00:18:38.743
...it was quite close...

00:18:41.204 --> 00:18:43.873
If Bazuso's axe had not been cracked...

00:18:44.332 --> 00:18:47.377
...the weapon would
have decapitated you.

00:18:48.962 --> 00:18:49.754
Maybe.

00:18:51.131 --> 00:18:52.590
You are honest.

00:18:54.259 --> 00:18:56.010
Judging by your way of fighting...

00:18:56.594 --> 00:18:59.389
...it seems you
always put your life at risk.

00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:04.394
You never yield an inch...

00:19:04.727 --> 00:19:08.148
...even when faced with a monster
like Bazuso or the group led by Corkus.

00:19:11.651 --> 00:19:14.779
On the contrary, you recklessly
challenge them with your sword...

00:19:15.405 --> 00:19:17.157
You are brave, but...

00:19:17.615 --> 00:19:21.411
I believe you purposefully put your
life in danger, and seek the meaning...

00:19:21.619 --> 00:19:24.289
...of your existence
by battling to preserve it...

00:19:24.372 --> 00:19:25.748
That's what I felt...

00:19:30.003 --> 00:19:31.421
You are interesting...

00:19:32.172 --> 00:19:34.299
I find you very much to my liking.

00:19:35.383 --> 00:19:37.385
I want you to join us, Guts!

00:19:48.688 --> 00:19:50.023
What is this...

00:19:50.064 --> 00:19:51.065
He...

00:19:51.566 --> 00:19:53.693
Why is he telling me this?

00:19:55.695 --> 00:19:57.697
If I say no?

00:19:58.072 --> 00:19:59.199
You don't want to?

00:20:00.325 --> 00:20:01.951
Of course not, I refuse!

00:20:07.832 --> 00:20:10.168
Don't talk as if you know so much!

00:20:10.585 --> 00:20:12.587
What do you know about me?

00:20:12.837 --> 00:20:16.174
We've never talked before, how
could you know anything about me?

00:20:16.549 --> 00:20:18.051
I don't know much about you...

00:20:18.092 --> 00:20:19.469
I just have a feeling about this...

00:20:20.303 --> 00:20:22.222
You lousy...

00:20:23.848 --> 00:20:27.560
...acting so friendly,
after you stabbed me!

00:20:28.102 --> 00:20:29.938
It's you who started the fight!

00:20:30.104 --> 00:20:32.607
I am definitely not
going to forget about this!

00:20:33.107 --> 00:20:37.612
I don't expect you to forget about
what I did either, killing your comrades!

00:20:39.113 --> 00:20:41.616
You and I are obviously enemies...

00:20:42.450 --> 00:20:43.743
What do you want?

00:20:43.993 --> 00:20:45.954
Well, that's simple...

00:20:53.336 --> 00:20:54.879
...to settle things with our swords.

00:20:56.256 --> 00:21:00.468
When I win, I'll make a hole
in your chest just like this one!

00:21:01.886 --> 00:21:03.388
What if I win?

00:21:03.721 --> 00:21:05.765
Do whatever you want with me!

00:21:07.141 --> 00:21:08.601
All right...

00:21:14.524 --> 00:21:17.527
I rather enjoy settling things by force...

00:21:17.735 --> 00:21:18.528
Griffith!

00:21:20.029 --> 00:21:21.531
Leave us alone, Caska.

00:21:21.864 --> 00:21:22.907
B-But...

00:21:23.866 --> 00:21:26.411
No matter what,
I will have what I want.

00:21:27.412 --> 00:21:29.914
I've had enough of
you acting so stuck up...

00:21:30.790 --> 00:21:32.542
...it makes me sick!

00:22:02.947 --> 00:22:05.074
<i>Looking back, the morning comes.</i>

